#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Bazı Xiaomi telefonları <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/"
#~ "sep/22/lithuania-tells-citizens-to-throw-out-chinese-phones-over-"
#~ "censorship-concerns\">Çin'in beğenmediği beyan edilen politik görüşlerden "
